description: Ministers are to discuss a "green list" of countries from where rules may be relaxed for travellers.
title: Coronavirus: Ireland accused of mixed message on foreign travel
title_page: Coronavirus: Ireland accused of mixed message on foreign travel - BBC News
maintext: It was first thought that about 20 countries would be included on the green list, but after a draft list was drawn up on Monday night, it is now expected that fewer than 12 will be included in the arrangement.
